<p>MySQL database setup:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Database</strong>: <code>bixcash_db</code></li>
<li><strong>User</strong>: <code>bixcash</code> (configured in <code>.env</code>)</li>
<li><strong>Connection</strong>: Standard Laravel database configuration</li>
<li><strong>Storage</strong>: Database sessions, cache, and queue</li>
</ul>
